{"tid":1534312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實我想有幾個站啲新閘係碌鳩已經縮咗入去直行直出就得","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T03:23:38.000Z","uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d9576a48234b80ad75d2ff8e03efea4b0fe6beb4","tid":1534312,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:19:12.000Z","msg":"所以分分鐘多加留意嘅話係連跳同推都慳返<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec89867b015ada94eca95ca4835a4825818c82a6","tid":1534312,"uid":285855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:20:41.000Z","msg":"香港回歸未定案嫁<br />\n<br />\n借一下位, 純手動po請見諒<br />\n<br />\n侵侵叫大陸還清朝債卷<br />\n大陸唔肯還成10萬億美金<br />\n佢話前朝唔認佢要還<br />\n如果唔駛還唔認點解要還香港<br />\nbloomberg同台灣都有講, 點解香港無聲氣<br />\n還, 大陸還唔起<br />\n唔還我地仲係英殖地<br />\n如果借據美國買左我地係美殖地<br />\n就算還都應該係還俾有還錢的政府, 我地就係台灣人<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2019-08-29%2Ftrump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=840720f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2019-08-29/trump-s-new-trade-war-weapon-might-just-be-antique-china-debt</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DzdS50W9Aq_Y&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=2927ab98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=zdS50W9Aq_Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1534137/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT7RnZZ8.png&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=4a044644\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://na.cx/i/T7RnZZ8.png</a>"},{"pid":"d828f6b2d8c275eb86e7c37880dd399737f87561","tid":1534312,"uid":143699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:22:09.000Z","msg":"大家冇需要再俾錢搭黨鐵啦，直接跳啦。大家唔好有任何嘅心理壓力，721，呢個月嘅封站，再加上太子站黨鐵嘅處理手法。佢唔再值得香港人俾一分一毫，我地一於全民跳閘<br />\n<br />\n1.呢隻係最簡單嘅跳法，肥啲都跳到，手腳並用，真係冇難度架，跳多兩次就會熟手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Aimi1zO.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimi1zO.gif&h=e6d946f6&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2.呢隻係新閘機，跳嘅時侯部機會響，要快手啲。同埋佢閘之間嘅距離有啲遠。用第一種跳法可能冇咁就手，建議直接跳過去，可以加個小助跑，都唔會太難。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iETUzUQ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiETUzUQ.gif&h=c8f39564&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 呢種方法會比較安全。因為直接跳閘點都會有cctv影到，但係跳欄杆嘅話可以搵啲盲位／暗位，難啲發現。不過跳嘅難度會比較高。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tRMSmzS.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtRMSmzS.gif&h=73d4b461&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同場加映錯誤示範</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MBkjO1B.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMBkjO1B.gif&h=c106dd4c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢位狗狗好明顯冇睇教學片啦，大家千奇唔好學佢啊，動作要標準。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注意事項：<br />\n－最好帶返口罩，遮一遮，保障返自已<br />\n－唔洗驚俾人捉到，就算俾人發現咗都可以直接跑走唔理佢，佢唔會真係追你9條街，當你離開咗佢個站嘅範圍，佢冇權捉你<br />\n－入閘時睇清楚有冇黃衫或可疑人士。真係得自已一個可以直接用第三招跳，最難捉。<br />\n－出閘嘅時侯更加唔洗驚，跳完係最近嘅出口快快手走人就得，唔會捉到你。<br />\n－其實仲有個安全啲嘅出閘方法，出閘果陣去客務到同佢講話岩岩係邊個邊個站嚟，但係跌咗張飛，問佢點算。你扮下野佢多數會俾一張一次性嘅綠色出閘卡你。我試過用呢招幾次都成功。<br />\n－黃衫人都係打份工，唔會同你咁搏命，都係果句，俾人捉到，大膽啲跑走唔好理佢<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌你老母狗鐵，你唔配收香港人錢呀。一齊跳佢老母閪！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完整示範片段：\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpLjuuYOyhk8%3Flist%3DLLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=7a802ed8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pLjuuYOyhk8?list=LLDdGX5puzbpkSMVfjKqEnEA</a>"},{"pid":"97af2e9a9da15d00bdbc2c08c13aaf42e3f6e15f","tid":1534312,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:23:38.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}